summary: RTX secures a $161M contract to support AIM-9X missile production, adding engineering work, warheads and tactical missile deliveries.

headline: Dr. Ronald Sugar and Gilman Louie join Ursa Major's Board of Directors
summary: Ursa Major today announced the appointment of Dr. Ronald Sugar and Gilman Louie to its Board of Directors, continuing the company's growth path to becoming a key provider of hypersonics, solid rocket motors, in-space propulsion, and launch systems.
